<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 10:08:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>国际劳工组织表示，随着气候变化，世界工人面临的风险越来越大</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/worlds-workers-increasingly-at-risk-as-climate-changes-ilo-says/articleshow/109499457.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109499457.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;全球劳动力面临着不断升级的气候风险，工人容易受到紫外线辐射和空气污染等各种危害的影响。政府需要采取紧急行动，保护工人免受气候相关疾病和死亡的影响。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:44:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/worlds-workers-increasingly-at-risk-as-climate-changes-ilo-says/articleshow/109499457.cms</guid></item><item><title>报告称，欧洲是变暖最快的大陆，几乎是全球平均速度的两倍</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/europe-is-the-fastest-warming-continent-at-nearly-twice-the-average-global-rate-report-says/articleshow/109499184.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109499184.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;欧洲面临气候变化导致的气温快速上升、健康风险和经济损失。向可再生能源过渡至关重要。尽管一些地区的气温低于平均水平，但对全球变暖后果的担忧仍然存在。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:35:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/europe-is-the-fastest-warming-continent-at-nearly-twice-the-average-global-rate-report-says/articleshow/109499184.cms</guid></item><item><title>台湾东部县发生地震</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwan-rattled-by-earthquake-in-eastern-county/articleshow/109498951.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109498951.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;台湾气象局称，台湾东部花莲县周一发生 5.5 级地震，目前尚未收到受损情况报告。本月早些时候，花莲发生里氏7.2级地震，造成至少14人死亡，此后台湾又发生了数百次余震。台湾位于两个板块交界处，地震频发。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:28:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwan-rattled-by-earthquake-in-eastern-county/articleshow/109498951.cms</guid></item><item><title>在习近平的领导下，中国间谍机构认为外国威胁“无处不在”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-ministry-of-state-security-mss-xi-jiping-chinas-spy-agency/articleshow/109490898.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109490898.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;对国家安全的高度关注是习近平强调外部威胁战略的一部分，一些分析人士认为这是转移国内对其政策批评的一种策略。这种方法包括扩大中国反间谍法中间谍活动的定义，创造一个更广泛的范围，可以影响正常的商业活动并加强国内的监视。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 05:36:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-ministry-of-state-security-mss-xi-jiping-chinas-spy-agency/articleshow/109490898.cms</guid></item><item><title>哥伦比亚大学因反以色列抗议而取消课程</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/columbia-university-cancels-classes-amid-anti-israel-protests/articleshow/109498604.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109498604.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:25:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/columbia-university-cancels-classes-amid-anti-israel-protests/articleshow/109498604.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗总统抵达伊斯兰堡开始为期三天的访问后与巴基斯坦总理举行会谈</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-president-holds-talks-with-pakistani-premier-after-arrival-in-islamabad-for-a-3-day-visit/articleshow/109498164.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109498164.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:06:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-president-holds-talks-with-pakistani-premier-after-arrival-in-islamabad-for-a-3-day-visit/articleshow/109498164.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列 Netzah Yehuda 营被指控什么？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/what-is-the-israeli-netzah-yehuda-battalion-accused-of/articleshow/109497729.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109497729.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据以色列媒体报道，美国将对以色列内扎·耶胡达营实施制裁，原因是其对待约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人的方式。以色列政府创建该营作为这些群体在军队服役的途径，允许他们维持宗教习俗，例如给他们祈祷和学习的时间，并限制他们与女兵的互动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 08:54:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/what-is-the-israeli-netzah-yehuda-battalion-accused-of/articleshow/109497729.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列军事情报局长因未能阻止 10 月 7 日袭击事件而辞职</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-military-intelligence-chief-resigns-over-failure-to-prevent-october-7-attack/articleshow/109495607.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109495607.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;阿哈龙·哈利瓦少将的辞职为以色列最高安全官员预计将因哈马斯的袭击造成更大影响奠定了基础，当时武装分子炸毁了以色列的边境防御工事，在数小时内毫无抵抗地横冲直撞地闯入以色列社区，造成 1,200 人死亡，其中大多数是平民，并劫持了大约 250 名人质进入加沙。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 07:53:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-military-intelligence-chief-resigns-over-failure-to-prevent-october-7-attack/articleshow/109495607.cms</guid></item><item><title>朝鲜向东海岸发射“数枚”弹道导弹</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-korea-launches-several-ballistic-missiles-towards-east-coast/articleshow/109496221.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109496221.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;朝鲜向韩国东海岸发射弹道导弹。日本当局证实在日本专属经济区外发射了短程导弹。对朝鲜在导弹开发工作中与莫斯科合作的担忧。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 08:28:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-korea-launches-several-ballistic-missiles-towards-east-coast/articleshow/109496221.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴布亚新几内亚总理驳斥拜登关于同类相食的“宽松”言论，称其为“模糊时刻”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/papua-new-guinea-pm-dismisses-bidens-loose-talk-on-cannibalism-as-a-blurry-moment/articleshow/109489215.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109489215.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;马拉佩驳斥了拜登关于芬尼根的同类相食的说法，强调了牢固的联系。记录显示芬尼根的飞机在海上迫降。拜登与特朗普、科尔、密特朗、马克龙的失态凸显。巴布亚新几内亚的同类相食历史，二战军火危害危急。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 04:35:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/papua-new-guinea-pm-dismisses-bidens-loose-talk-on-cannibalism-as-a-blurry-moment/articleshow/109489215.cms</guid></item><item><title>官员表示，中国致力于通过对话解决海上争端</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-is-committed-to-resolving-maritime-disputes-through-talks-official-says/articleshow/109488292.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109488292.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周一，一名高级军事官员在港口城市青岛举行的外国海军高级官员会议上表示，中国仍致力于通过对话解决与其他国家的海上问题，但不会被“滥用”。中央军委副主席、习近平主席的亲密盟友张又侠表示，海上不应该成为各国展示“炮舰肌肉”的舞台。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 03:52:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/china-is-committed-to-resolving-maritime-disputes-through-talks-official-says/articleshow/109488292.cms</guid></item><item><title>SIPRI报告：冲突将军费开支推至“历史新高”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/conflicts-push-military-spending-to-all-time-high-sipri-report/articleshow/109488551.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109488551.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 2023年，在战争和紧张局势加剧的推动下，全球军费开支创下2.4万亿美元的新高。所有地区都增加了军费开支，其中美国和中国领先。未来预计在全球局势持续升级的情况下将进一步增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 04:10:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/conflicts-push-military-spending-to-all-time-high-sipri-report/articleshow/109488551.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦奎达和卡拉奇的污水样本中检测到更多脊髓灰质炎病毒</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/more-poliovirus-detected-in-sewage-samples-from-pakistans-quetta-karachi/articleshow/109487628.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109487628.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦奎达和卡拉奇地区检测到 1 型野生脊髓灰质炎病毒，该病毒与先前根除的病毒群有关。 2023 年病毒的重新引入与阿富汗的 YB3A 集群有关。在合作伙伴和捐助者的大力支持下，阻断脊髓灰质炎病毒传播的努力仍在继续。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 03:50:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/more-poliovirus-detected-in-sewage-samples-from-pakistans-quetta-karachi/articleshow/109487628.cms</guid></item><item><title>天琴座流星雨：观看时间和地点</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/lyrid-meteor-shower-when-and-where-to-watch/articleshow/109487824.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109487824.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;天琴座流星雨周日达到顶峰，从北半球观看效果最佳。美国宇航局 (NASA) 注意到天琴座流星雨已有 2,700 年的历史。月亮的亮度可能会影响能见度。 EarthSky 提到每小时有多达 100 颗流星激增。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 03:37:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/science/lyrid-meteor-shower-when-and-where-to-watch/articleshow/109487824.cms</guid></item><item><title>暴风雨袭击华南地区 11人失踪 数万人疏散</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/11-missing-tens-of-thousands-evacuated-as-storms-strike-south-china/articleshow/109487584.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109487584.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国南方有11人因暴风雨失踪，广东数千人撤离。新华社报道称，清远市已有 11 人失踪，超过 45,000 人已被疏散。全省已转移安置群众5.3万余人。预计周一大雨持续，气象部门预计贵州深圳有雷阵雨。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 03:33:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/11-missing-tens-of-thousands-evacuated-as-storms-strike-south-china/articleshow/109487584.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦：议会大厦清真寺20双鞋被盗</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-20-pairs-of-shoes-stolen-from-mosque-in-parliament-complex/articleshow/109487392.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109487392.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;这一事件发生在周五议会大厦内一座清真寺的祈祷期间，包括国民议会议员（MNA）、记者和议会工作人员在内的礼拜者聚集在那里。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 03:20:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-20-pairs-of-shoes-stolen-from-mosque-in-parliament-complex/articleshow/109487392.cms</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚蘑菇谋杀案嫌疑人将于五月出庭受审</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australian-mushroom-murder-suspect-to-face-court-in-may/articleshow/109486585.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109486585.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;艾琳·帕特森 (Erin Patterson) 因在 2023 年 7 月用有毒的蘑菇惠灵顿牛肉毒害她的姻亲和牧师的妻子而面临谋杀指控。该案涉及 5 月份的移交，受害者包括唐·帕特森 (Don and Gail Patterson) 和盖尔·帕特森 (Gail Patterson) 以及伊恩·威尔金森 (Ian Wilkinson)。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:56:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/australian-mushroom-murder-suspect-to-face-court-in-may/articleshow/109486585.cms</guid></item><item><title>报告称，欧洲是变暖最快的大陆，几乎是全球平均速度的两倍</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/environment/europe-is-the-fastest-warming-continent-at-nearly-twice-the-average-global-rate-report-says/articleshow/109486437.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109486437.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;欧洲面临气温上升、极端气候和健康影响。向可再生能源转型对于应对后果至关重要。死亡与气温上升有关。非洲大陆极端气候事件造成的经济损失。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:37:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/home/environment/europe-is-the-fastest-warming-continent-at-nearly-twice-the-average-global-rate-report-says/articleshow/109486437.cms</guid></item><item><title>埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）对 X 上的悉尼袭击图像引起了澳大利亚的愤怒</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/elon-musk-draws-australias-wrath-over-sydney-attack-images-on-x/articleshow/109486132.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109486132.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;澳大利亚正准备与埃隆·马斯克和其他美国社交媒体公司对峙，因为它们在管理过去十天内发生在悉尼的两起暴力事件相关的露骨内容和错误信息方面反应迟缓。澳大利亚政府通过三位部长建议引入更严格的法规，包括针对这些平台的强制性行为准则。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:18:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/elon-musk-draws-australias-wrath-over-sydney-attack-images-on-x/articleshow/109486132.cms</guid></item><item><title>曾被囚禁在中东的美国记者特里·安德森去世，享年76岁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-journalist-terry-anderson-once-held-captive-in-mideast-dies-at-76/articleshow/109485969.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109485969.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国记者特里·安德森于1985年在黎巴嫩被伊斯兰武装分子绑架，并被囚禁了六年，于周日去世，享年76岁。安德森被绑架时担任美联社贝鲁特分社社长，他保持着黎巴嫩被扣押时间最长的西方人质的记录，直到 1991 年最终获释。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:00:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-journalist-terry-anderson-once-held-captive-in-mideast-dies-at-76/articleshow/109485969.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>